OL,5, Vogue's former creative director and   
OL,6, editor-at-large Andre Leon Talley has  
OL,7, died at the age of 73.                 
OL,9,FThe fashion journalist, whose career   
OL,10,Fspanned five decades, died on Tuesday  
OL,11,Fin New York, his representatives said. 
OL,13,FA statement on his Instagram page      
OL,14,Fconfirmed his death "with great        
OL,15,Fsadness" and described Talley as a     
OL,16,F"larger-than-life" figure.             
OL,18,FVogue editor-in-chief Anna Wintour     
OL,19,Fremembered him fondly as "magnificent  
OL,20,Fand erudite and wickedly funny".       
